      "message": "Utilization is not defined in the upstream PDI for xyz.openbmc_project.Inventory.Item.Cpu.OperatingConfig (OperatingConfig.interface.yaml).\nhttps://github.com/openbmc/phosphor-dbus-interfaces/blob/master/yaml/xyz/openbmc_project/Inventory/Item/Cpu/OperatingConfig.interface.yaml",
